# FOSS & Privacy Compliance

## License

- **Apache-2.0** — F-Droid-only distribution
- No proprietary closed-source SDKs in production path
- Android: no Google Play Services, Firebase, or closed telemetry trackers

## Network

- **No `INTERNET` permission** in release manifest
- External links via `ACTION_VIEW` only (donate, changelog)

## Privacy

- All data local on device; no cloud, no analytics
- Notification listener reads metadata locally for attribution only

## Security

- Root: libsu in-app only; command allowlist — no user input in shell
- New Gradle deps: check [`docs/FOSS.md`](docs/FOSS.md)

## Android FOSS

- Reproducible builds — `scripts/fdroid/verify-reproducible.sh`
- Lock Gradle wrapper and dependency versions
